enb_long_title: Sixteenth Sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies
sentences: In the conclusions (FCCC/SBSTA/2002/CRP.2), the SBSTA agrees to continue consideration of the item at SB-17, including the need for, timing of and elements for possible workshops and the possibility of holding an initial workshop before SB-19.
The conclusions request the Secretariat to consider Article 2.3 in the compilation of information on P&Ms of Annex I Parties in the third national communications of Annex I Parties.
